TIGER LAW ORDER LLC invites responsible employees to guard sensitive facilities in Vladivostok.

Candidates who have successfully completed a contract with the TIGER volunteer detachment and have experience in the Northern Military District are considered first.

We offer:
- Official employment;
- Work schedule 1/3 (every three days);
-Stable salary (RUB 70,000);
- Assistance in obtaining the 6th rank of security guard;
- Providing uniforms;
- Opportunity for training, advanced training and career growth.

Requirements:
- Age 20-60 years;
- Normal physical shape;
- Responsible and disciplined attitude to work, decency, diligence, learning ability.
- Knowledge of safety principles and security rules, legal literacy.

